I can show...

872
01:09:42,480 --> 01:09:44,880
你在開玩笑吧
Oh, you gotta be kidding me.

873
01:09:46,430 --> 01:09:48,330
你說過你不會傷害俘虜的
You said you wouldn't hurt the prisoners.

874
